title: New Point of Acceptance
content: We are very pleased that «Bewegte Integration» is part of the Leu ecosystem. Moving Integration offers systemic constellations to look at personal obstacles.  More information can be found on our website.

title: Endorse your Friends
content: Guarantee your friends & colleagues access to the community income by giving them an endorsment.

title: Leu Cycles: New Time
content: Fom September 5th onwards, the cycles will be held at 6 pm. This change will allow more people to participate. The schedule remains unchanged, as well as the rhythm every 10 days. You can find the information in detail on the website. As usual; direclty afterwards we'll meet at L200.
